</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BB1D67CFFE71E2681E8FEF200CC8AB8" blockId="21.[714,1247,256,484]" pageId="21" pageNumber="80">
<emphasis id="B97A0A6EFFE71E2681E8FEF200168A95" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="80">
Plantae 
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E26803FFEF300A98A4B" box="[819,912,256,280]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.25" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="cm" value="22.5" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="15.0">15-30 cm</quantity>
altae, caule bene supra terram producto, cormo 
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E268045FEEA00968A6D" box="[841,943,281,305]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" metricValueMax="1.5" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="mm" value="12.5" valueMax="15.0" valueMin="10.0">10-15 mm</quantity>
diam., foliis 2 vel 3, basali solitario, filiformibus in sectione transversali ovalibus 4-sulcatis, inflorescentiae bracteis exterioribus viridibus marginibus et apice membranaceis, interioribus marginibus late membranaceis, floribus albis cupula 
<taxonomicName id="4C0EADFFFFE71E268775FE7307938AC4" box="[1145,1194,384,408]" class="Liliopsida" family="Iridaceae" genus="Romuleae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asparagales" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="flava">flava</taxonomicName>
, tubo perianthii infundibuliformi, 
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E2680D7FE6A07118AF3" box="[987,1064,408,433]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5-6 mm</quantity>
longo, tepalis ellipticis 25-28
</emphasis>
× 
<emphasis id="B97A0A6EFFE71E268044FE4200CC8AB8" italics="true" pageId="21" pageNumber="80">
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E268044FE4200AF8A95" box="[840,918,433,457]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="7.5" metricValueMax="8.0" metricValueMin="7.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="mm" value="7.5" valueMax="8.0" valueMin="7.0">7-8 mm</quantity>
, filamentis 
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E26870EFE4107778A95" box="[1026,1102,434,458]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="5.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="mm" value="5.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="5.0">5-6 mm</quantity>
longis, antheris contiguis 
<quantity id="4CF67B99FFE71E26802EFE3900428ABE" box="[802,891,458,482]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="8.0" pageId="21" pageNumber="80" unit="mm" value="9.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="8.0">8-10 mm</quantity>
longis flavis.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
